
----------Useful commands----------

pip list --local

pip install -r requirements.txt

python manage.py makemigrations api

python manage.py migrate

python manage.py runserver

python manage.py showmigrations

python manage.py migrate --fake api zero

#SUPER USER for admin panel
python manage.py createsuperuser
#then go to localhost/admin

Pre-populating database (no way was found to load the files in 1 command):

python manage.py loaddata util\fixtures\continent.json
python manage.py loaddata util\fixtures\country.json
python manage.py loaddata util\fixtures\city.json
python manage.py loaddata profiles\fixtures\user.json
python manage.py loaddata profiles\fixtures\profile.json

Destroying data in the whole database:
python manage.py flush



